text: Nice location and near to Holland Road MRT with a bus stop in front! Holland Village is walking distance. Also, because of low density it is private and quiet. It has a small pool and gym too.
Convenient location with Bus outside, MRT walking distance. Botanic Gardens, wet market, amenities nearby. Small cozy development with no noisy kids because it does not have a playground.
Good location..nice environment..bus stop is in the in front of the building..quite far from MRT station
Okay! The security workers are amicable. Manager can be better.
